    "body": "The png loader assumes that all UI sprites are 32 bit, which is true for the upstream mods.\r\n\r\nIt shouldn't be hard to have it automatically upgrade 8 or 24 bit images to 32 bit on load, but obviously there will be a performance overhead here (which you would have been paying already with the System.Drawing loader)."
